HEADWORD: Surfy
<hw>Surf"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Consisting of,
abounding in, or resembling, surf; <as>as, a <ex>surfy</ex>
shore</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Scarce had they cleared the <qex>surfy</qex> waves⟦br⟧
That foam around those frightful caves.</q>
<rj><qau>Moore.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Surge</ent>⟦br⟧
